    <h1>The Benefits of Natural Skincare</h1>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="author">By Jane Smith</div>
      <time datetime="2025-05-14">May 14, 2025</time>
      <div class="tags">
        <span class="tag">Skincare</span>
